{"tid":2156201,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"諗起早兩年同個女仔食飯 佢無俾錢","createTime":"2020-08-14T09:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T10:30:48.000Z","uid":177089,"like":48,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c389302d31c64734d424b73f6f93f90277065e4d","tid":2156201,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的 個時frd搭frd識咗個肥婆 <br />\n諗住肥婆都係肉 照溝住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就約咗佢去食元氣啦 唔好屌我住 都話曬兩三年前<br />\n<br />\n好記得個餐兩條友友都食咗成4舊水 <br />\n咁佢俾返一半好正常呀？<br />\n仆佢個街真係夠膽死我唔講起佢就唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一話俾錢佢就起身走咗佢<br />\n做肥婆做到咁無道德我都係第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到門口我又唔好意思問佢拎返 就咁俾佢屈咗一餐<br />\n返到屋企心生不憤 就影低咗張單 諗住第時可以claim返佢<br />\n結果之後都無再搵過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得如果我有張單 佢又差我錢<br />\n應唔應該去小額錢債claim佢老母？<br />\n<br />\n應該 肥婆食飯係應該俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔應該 兩三年前嘅野好心咪咁小氣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dea88336468046dd84eca81b40ce29d8fdba26b","tid":2156201,"uid":311910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"上佢屋企搵佢"},{"pid":"d0c22be49610bfc93b22abc068329b285228a4a1","tid":2156201,"uid":311910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"null"},{"pid":"808c6db0c1be2eaa6690c792cee94242234378bd","tid":2156201,"uid":35539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"睇下佢隻雞有冇甩哂毛"},{"pid":"8166720c7aac391d75dc5535d1878e92b4785c82","tid":2156201,"uid":41368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"啱啊claim 佢lm啦<br />\n我次次搭的士都蝕幾毫子俾司機<br />\n依家